\v 5 \w Esta|strong="H2088"\w* \w es|strong="H1931"\w* \w la|strong="H1931"\w* copa de \w la|strong="H1931"\w* \w que|strong="H1931"\w* \w él|strong="H1931"\w* personalmente \w bebe|strong="H8354"\w*, y \w que|strong="H1931"\w* usa para \w adivinar|strong="H5172"\w*.\f + \fr 44.5  \ft “Divination”: a way of discovering secrets or hidden knowledge. Sometimes this is close to magic, but, in this case, it may be that José is using a common superstition to cover up his plan.\f* \w Lo|strong="H1931"\w* \w que|strong="H1931"\w* han \w hecho|strong="H6213"\w* \w es|strong="H1931"\w* realmente malo!’” 
